# ================================================================
# NOTES FOR DEPLOYMENT
# ================================================================
# 
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (XAMPP):
# - Keep display_errors On
# - session.cookie_secure should be 0 (no HTTPS)
# - RewriteBase should match your folder name
# 
# PRODUCTION (InfinityFree/000WebHost):
# - Change display_errors to Off
# - Enable HTTPS redirect if you have SSL
# - Change session.cookie_secure to 1 if using HTTPS
# - Update RewriteBase if needed
# - Consider enabling Content-Security-Policy
# 
# ================================================================